                    <span>I "stumbled" in to Search Engine Marketing and now "do it" for a living with car dealerships in the San Francisco Bay Area.<p>This book, in it's first few pages, helped me. NO I don't know the author :)<p>David Saunders, Concord, CA</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Want to learn about true, effective marketing...read this!</div>
