                    <span>So there are steps in every transaction. The whole point of this book is that you don't create lifelong relationships with strangers. Every sale consists of multiple mini sales. <br>turn the page<br>click the link...<p>You go to amazon<br>browse through books<br>see related books<br>browse through reviews<br>buy the book<p>While some of the data relating to the internet is outdated, the fundamental message of the book is still strong. Those who think traditional media outpace targeted ads are dead wrong.</span>
                  
